<title>USA: Atlantic Beverage CEO set employment pact.</title>
<headline>Atlantic Beverage CEO set employment pact.</headline>
<dateline>BALTIMORE 1996-11-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Atlantic Beverage Co Inc said on Friday that it executed a long-term employment agreement with Alan Sussna, 39, to continue serving as president and chief executive officer.</p>
<p>The company also said it would establish its corporate office to oversee the food and beverages businesses in Northbrook, Illinois, and that Sussna would be based there.</p>
<p>Sussna joined Atlantic Beverage in March 1996 and was previously a partner in the consulting firms of McKinsey &amp; Co and Bain &amp; Co.</p>
<p>-- New York newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
